sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User
participant App as Look Graph Webview
participant Router as GraphMessageRouter
participant Registry as RepositoryRegistry
participant UseCase as GetGraphDataUseCase
participant SubmoduleRepo as Initialized Submodule GitRepository implements GitHistoryOperations
participant Runtime as HybridGitRuntime
participant Cli as CliGitRuntime

User->>App: Select submodule node
App->>Router: graph/dataRequest(submoduleRepositoryLocator, PageRequest, filters, requestId)
Router->>Registry: resolveRepository(submoduleRepositoryLocator)
alt submodule repository is initialized
  Registry-->>Router: SubmoduleRepo
  Router->>UseCase: execute(SubmoduleRepo, filters, PageRequest, signal)
  UseCase->>SubmoduleRepo: getCommitGraph(filters, PageRequest, signal)
  SubmoduleRepo->>Runtime: getCommitGraph(executionContext, filters, PageRequest, signal)
  Runtime->>Cli: getCommitGraph(executionContext, filters, PageRequest, signal)
  Cli-->>Runtime: Page(GitCommit)
  Runtime-->>SubmoduleRepo: Page(GitCommit)
  SubmoduleRepo-->>UseCase: Page(GitCommit)
  UseCase-->>Router: GraphData
  Router-->>App: graph/dataResponse(requestId, GraphData)
  App-->>User: Render submodule repository graph
else submodule repository is not initialized
  Registry-->>Router: not initialized
  Router-->>App: graph/error(requestId, notInitialized)
end
